 36→
 37→Respond ONLY with a JSON object in this exact format:
 38→{
 39→  "category": "CODE|REASONING|SIMPLE|CLOUD",
 40→  "confidence": 0.0-1.0,
 41→  "reasoning": "Brief explanation"
 42→}
 43→
 44→Be concise. No additional text.`;
